    <!-- FAQ -->
    <section id="faq" class="py-16">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-display font-bold text-gray-900 text-center mb-12">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
            
            <div class="mb-8">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-av-gold mb-4">Getting Started</h3>
                <div class="space-y-4">
                    <details class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-200 p-6 group">
                        <summary class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer font-semibold text-gray-900">How do I install Arsenal Vault?<i class="bi bi-chevron-down text-av-gold group-open:rotate-180 transition"></i></summary>
                        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">Download the installer from our download page, run it, and follow the on-screen instructions. The installation takes less than a minute. <a href="support/windows-install.html" class="text-av-gold hover:underline">See our detailed Windows 11 installation guide →</a></p>
                    </details>
                    <details class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-200 p-6 group">
                        <summary class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer font-semibold text-gray-900">Is Arsenal Vault available now?<i class="bi bi-chevron-down text-av-gold group-open:rotate-180 transition"></i></summary>
                        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">Yes! Arsenal Vault is available now. Download the Desktop app from our <a href="download.html" class="text-av-gold hover:underline">download page</a>, or create a Free Forever account for the <a href="https://app.arsenalvault.com/register?utm_source=arsenalvault.com&utm_medium=site_cta&utm_campaign=free_account" class="text-av-gold hover:underline">cloud version</a>.</p>
                    </details>
                    <details class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-200 p-6 group">
                        <summary class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer font-semibold text-gray-900">Can I import data from other software?<i class="bi bi-chevron-down text-av-gold group-open:rotate-180 transition"></i></summary>
                        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">Yes, Arsenal Vault supports CSV import for easy data migration. We have guides for migrating from popular alternatives including spreadsheets and other inventory apps.</p>
                    </details>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="mb-8">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-av-gold mb-4">Features & Usage</h3>
                <div class="space-y-4">
                    <details class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-200 p-6 group">
                        <summary class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer font-semibold text-gray-900">How do I add photos to my inventory?<i class="bi bi-chevron-down text-av-gold group-open:rotate-180 transition"></i></summary>
                        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">When viewing or editing any item, click the "Photos" tab and use the upload button. You can add multiple photos per item, and they'll be automatically resized for optimal storage.</p>
                    </details>
                    <details class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-200 p-6 group">
                        <summary class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer font-semibold text-gray-900">Can I generate reports for insurance?<i class="bi bi-chevron-down text-av-gold group-open:rotate-180 transition"></i></summary>
                        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">Yes! Go to Reports > Collection Overview to generate a comprehensive PDF report with photos, serial numbers, and values. This is perfect for insurance documentation.</p>
                    </details>
                    <details class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-200 p-6 group">
                        <summary class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer font-semibold text-gray-900">What are the 15 parts categories?<i class="bi bi-chevron-down text-av-gold group-open:rotate-180 transition"></i></summary>
                        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">Arsenal Vault includes categories for: Barrels, Triggers, Stocks & Grips, Optics & Sights, Magazines, Muzzle Devices, Handguards & Rails, Bolts & Carriers, Lowers & Receivers, Uppers, Springs & Pins, Lights & Lasers, Furniture, Suppressors, and Other Parts.</p>
                    </details>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="mb-8">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-av-gold mb-4">Security & Privacy</h3>
                <div class="space-y-4">
                    <details class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-200 p-6 group">
                        <summary class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer font-semibold text-gray-900">Is my data secure?<i class="bi bi-chevron-down text-av-gold group-open:rotate-180 transition"></i></summary>
                        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">Absolutely. For desktop users, all data stays on your local machine. Cloud data is encrypted in transit and at rest, with sensitive fields like serial numbers protected by additional encryption layers. <a href="security.html" class="text-av-gold hover:underline">Read the security details →</a></p>
                    </details>
                    <details class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-200 p-6 group">
                        <summary class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer font-semibold text-gray-900">Do you share or sell my data?<i class="bi bi-chevron-down text-av-gold group-open:rotate-180 transition"></i></summary>
                        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">Never. Your inventory data is yours alone. We don't share, sell, or analyze your collection data for any purpose. See our <a href="legal.html#pp" class="text-av-gold hover:underline">Privacy Policy</a> for complete details.</p>
                    </details>
                    <details class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-200 p-6 group">
                        <summary class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer font-semibold text-gray-900">How do I backup my data?<i class="bi bi-chevron-down text-av-gold group-open:rotate-180 transition"></i></summary>
                        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">For desktop users, go to Admin > Backup to create a complete backup file. Cloud users have automatic daily backups with the ability to download their data at any time.</p>
                    </details>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-av-gold mb-4">Billing & Account</h3>
                <div class="space-y-4">
                    <details class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-200 p-6 group">
                        <summary class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer font-semibold text-gray-900">What's your refund policy?<i class="bi bi-chevron-down text-av-gold group-open:rotate-180 transition"></i></summary>
                        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">Cloud plans include a free forever account. For desktop license questions or billing issues, contact support and we'll help make it right.</p>
                    </details>
                    <details class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-200 p-6 group">
                        <summary class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer font-semibold text-gray-900">Can I upgrade from desktop to cloud?<i class="bi bi-chevron-down text-av-gold group-open:rotate-180 transition"></i></summary>
                        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">Yes! You can export your data from the desktop version and import it to a cloud account at any time. We also offer upgrade pricing for existing desktop customers.</p>
                    </details>
                    <details class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-200 p-6 group">
                        <summary class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer font-semibold text-gray-900">What payment methods do you accept?<i class="bi bi-chevron-down text-av-gold group-open:rotate-180 transition"></i></summary>
                        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">We accept major credit cards through our secure payment processor.</p>
                    </details>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

